This is basically Customer Record Management application.
The application contains following features:
1. Home screen with functionality to "Add Customer" or "Search"
2. "Add Customer" screen have fields Customer name, Email, Phone, Address, City, State, Pincode and Country.
3. "Search" screen allows search on name or phone or email and has search button and list of customers to be displayed below the above fields (for search results).
   On right click any of the customer from search results, the user should gets two options "Edit" and "Delete".
   The edit option allows editing of customer record and delete option deletes the customer record.